    'description' => 'Multi-source topic research tool: given a topic, searches Hacker News (via Algolia API), fetches Wikipedia summary, and fetches/strips web articles from the top results. Returns a consolidated structured report with HN discussions, Wikipedia abstract, and article excerpts. Uses PHP streams for all network calls. First cross-source research composition tool — orchestrates three independent data sources into one pipeline. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
